 Destructor saw the bleep on the screen. "Hydras we have another bot landed 
outside in a stasis pod I'll go check it out." DEstructor walked down the 
ramp and saaw the pod. The warning on the side caught him off guard. Proto 
showed up behind him. "Lets take it inside and examine it first....a messed 
up maximal is a dangerous predacon." They both grabbed the edge of the pod 
and pulled it into the ship and down the hall into the lab.
